{"about_the_game":"Have you ever wondered what your kitty will be dreaming about on New Year\u2019s Eve?<br><br>&quot;Fireworks Dream&quot; is a survivor Like game with the theme of fireworks. In the game, you will enter the dreamland of a kitten, which is full of dangers, but the only thing that can help it is - fireworks! You will help this kitten fight off monsters in the New Year's Eve nightmare, find clues to break the nightmare, and return to its owner.<br><br>In the game, you will experience:<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/BB1_CN.png?t=1707361981\" /><br>The game is based on the classic survivor gameplay framework. Upgrading, strengthening, and spawning monsters are still important parts of the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/LevelUP.gif?t=1707361981\" /><br>However, the weapons that can be used this time will be various types of fireworks that are common during the New Year festival.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/StarUP.gif?t=1707361981\" /><br>There seems to be some special chemical reactions between various fireworks weapons.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/Boud.gif?t=1707361981\" /><br>Maybe you can find a familiar figure among them, and of course there are some unique surprises waiting for you to discover.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/Jellyfish.gif?t=1707361981\" /><br>But please do not imitate the in-game operations in real life. ;)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/BB2_CN.png?t=1707361981\" /><br>The game will use simple interactions to tell a heart-warming story. The story revolves around the bond and emotional bond between the kitten and its owner, and demonstrates the kitten's overcoming of fear and cultivation of courage through the challenges of each dream.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/BB3_CN.png?t=1707361981\" /><br>I believe you will eventually help the kitten return to its owner, but you don\u2019t need to worry about the lonely time after sending the kitten away, because we have also prepared a fireworks viewing mode for you. In this mode you can freely adjust the fireworks you want to watch within certain limits.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/JellyfishView.gif?t=1707361981\" /><br>You can even launch fireworks yourself.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/FireworkBall.gif?t=1707361981\" /><br>Discover the fireworks show you most want to see!<br>In addition, we have also prepared a set of achievement patterns with a festive atmosphere, maybe you will need them.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2795120/extras/BB5_CN.png?t=1707361981\" /><br>Finally, make good use of the fireworks on hand and paint your dreams with a bright color during festivals that require fireworks!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u8ca1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2795120/b336e9f638b22bdadfaa41ff3278f1eec226524f.jpg"},{"name":"\u767c","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2795120/66ae6c609876f189a3f72512cd492cc85b61fe13.jpg"},{"name":"\u8d22","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2795120/929dcd01ea508fd08fc1928474bfe10987577fff.jpg"},{"name":"\u53d1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommu